  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Tzedek Law LLC is a boutique law firm in the conveyancing legal industry. We are able to provide growth for all employees in the firm and yet foster a cosy family style environment in the office.</p>\n<p>Responsibilities include assisting the lawyer and legal executives in real estate transactions, preparation of documents, Filing and scanning of documents, Handle calls, correspondence and confidential documents,<br>\nManage calendars and appointments of lawyer, Perform data entry, filing, photocopying and faxing,<br>\nPrepare invoices.Other ad hoc duties as assigned.</p>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<p>A team player and a meticulous individual with strong sense of responsibility, initiative and integrity,<br>\nGood communication and organisation skills,<br>\nComputer savvy,<br>\nGood command in English,<br>\nAbility to multi-task, and</p>\n<p>Overtime is NOT required, and flexible work hours is possible.</p>\n<p>Legal knowledge and prior experience is NOT required.</p>\n<p>Training will be provided.</p>",
